{"tid":2389094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★逾百年歷史 曾福琴行宣佈結業！！！","createTime":"2021-01-31T15:23:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T16:46:52.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d63eba4da054a1287cbfe0e69374bc53b50bb15c","tid":2389094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"在香港超過一百年歷史的曾福琴行，稱考慮到經營環境及接班問題，最近宣佈&ldquo;光榮結業&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  曾福琴行1916年在香港創立，創辦人曾福是廣東清遠人，十九世紀末來港後，在羅便臣鋼琴公司打工，跟公司技師學習調音。1916年，曾福在灣仔摩利臣山道開設首間曾福琴行，幫顧客調音及修理鋼琴，其後自行生產摩利臣牌子鋼琴，在本地售賣外，更外銷至英國、東南亞等地。<br />\n<br />\n  因琴行曾在北角七姊妹道設廠，廠房旁邊的街道亦因此命名&ldquo;琴行街&rdquo;。曾福琴行宣佈3月正式結業，遣散約20名員工。<br />\n<br />\n  曾福琴行負責人梁小姐表示，琴行上兩代人已經離世，第三代也已屆退休年齡，而第四代大部分已在外國定居，無意繼承事業，加之現時經營環境困難，因此決定結業。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2021/0131/876853.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2021%2F0131%2F876853.shtml&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G13VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=b3eb7292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2021/0131/876853.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"98cabec6fdce879385ed0114d12dcaa49ba6517e","tid":2389094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd580d81f500c7fc0e11f10ed58cb6bbbdc36d19","tid":2389094,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"曾福琴行宣佈3月正式結業，遣散約20名員工。"},{"pid":"67f91235c518c6359b64f936b05daf2c03fcb494","tid":2389094,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,